{"id":77602,"type":2,"name":"ふたりのジョー","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/95/e3/77602_DNDiN.jpg","rating":{"total":6,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":1,"5":4,"6":0,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":4.5},"summary":"　『あしたのジョー』や『巨人の星』など、数々の名作を作り上げた梶原一騎の遺作原案をアニメ化した作品。本作は、スポーツグラフ誌『Number』で連載されていたオリジナルボクシング小説で、全６話の構成となっている。\r\n　物語は、カリスマ的な人気ＤＪである結城譲と沖縄の貧困家庭に育った赤嶺丈、すべてが正反対の二人のジョーを中心に展開していく。ボクシングという過酷な世界で、二人はライバルとして拳を交えることになり……。名作『あしたのジョー』のレフレインさせるようなスポーツアクションアニメで、30年を経て新たな「ジョー」の物語が楽しめる。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>二人之丈</li><li><span>话数: </span>6</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/13470\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">高橋滋春</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>Futari no Joe</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Joe vs. Joe</li><li><span>发售日: </span>2003年5月25日</li><li><span>开始: </span>2003年5月25日</li><li><span>结束: </span>2003年9月25日</li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":10,"on_hold":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":4},{"name":"独立ova","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":293563,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/293563","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":293564,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/293564","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":293565,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/293565","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":293566,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/293566","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":293567,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/293567","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":293568,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/293568","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":13470,"image":"","name":"高桥滋春","desc":"导演"}]}